comments: Davis (LAL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Jackson (LAC) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Westbrook (LAL) hooks Jackson (LAC) on the drive and the contact affects his legal guarding position.
Monk (LAL) reaches in and makes contact to George's (LAC) arm that affects his ability to gather and enter his shooting motion.
Westbrook (LAL) maintains a legal pivot foot.
Jackson (LAC) places a hand/arm to Westbrook's (LAL) front at the start of the drive but the contact is marginal.
Monk (LAL) makes marginal contact with Ibaka's (LAC) arm off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Anthony (LAL) and Morris Sr. (LAC) get tangled during the screen off ball and the contact is marginal.
Ibaka (LAC) makes marginal contact to James' (LAL) body at the end of his drive that doesn't affect his SBQR.
Anthony (LAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
